data.description: This beautiful brick 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is in a great location and turn-key! Inside the home the entry leads to an open floor plan with living room, dining room and breakfast nook/office all centrally located near the kitchen, spacious enough for entertaining or family gatherings. The kitchen has granite countertops, custom cabinetry, Frigidaire appliances, hop-up bar, and utility room with pantry shelving. The spacious master bedroom has a walk-in closet and separate shower in master bathroom with garden tub. Additional interior features include luxury vinyl tile flooring throughout the main living and wet areas and LED lighting. Exterior features include covered porch that is accessible from the living room and master bedroom. Do you love low energy bills? This home comes equipped with Solar Panels! Schedule your private viewing today!
